These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta
There are 2 different nationalities: indonesian, italian
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: bellflower, aconite
City: rome, edinburgh
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the person who growsaconite##3
2. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
3. the italian is the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | fanta   |
| Nationality   | italian     | indonesian   |
| Flower         | aconite | bellflower |
| City     | rome | edinburgh    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, august
The people have 2 different jobs:  analyst, writer
2 different pets are kept: dog, rat
The people have 2 different hobbies: photography, sudoku
1. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
2. the analyst is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the writer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Birthday          | may     | august |
| Job   | writer | analyst  |
| Pet           | rat         | dog     |
| Hobby     | photography   | sudoku    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, singing
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, entrepreneur
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, chess
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, january
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
2. the person playing chess is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Hobby    | singing     | puzzles |
| Job         | entrepreneur | accountant    |
| Game         | mah-jongg         | chess        |
| Birthday   | may         | january    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, egyptian
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: martial-arts, epic
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, cooking
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, july
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
2. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the italian##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Nationality      | egyptian     | italian |
| Movie-Genre          | epic   | martial-arts  |
| Hobby         | card-games | cooking     |
| Birthday   | march  | july         |

