.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-5::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk
House: cape-cod, art-deco
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, helicopter
There are 2 different favourite colors: blood-red, pink
1. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person who likes pink is in an odd position##4
3. the art-deco house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | milk       |
| House           | art-deco      | cape-cod     |
| Transport   | helicopter       | bike   |
| Color           | pink          | blood-red |

