.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: begonia, rose
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: reggae, dubstep
There are 2 different favourite colors: red, azure
1. the person who likes azure is in an even position##4
2. the egyptian is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who growsrose is the dutch##1
4. the fan of reggae is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Flower           | rose | begonia    |
| Nationality   | dutch       | egyptian |
| Music-Genre           | reggae         | dubstep    |
| Color         | red    | azure   |

