The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, family
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the fan of house##1
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |
| City    | san-francisco       | berlin    |
| Hobby       | skydiving | drawing |
| Music-Genre         | house      | rock  |
| Movie-Genre   | family       | horror  |

