The people have 2 different hobbies: chess, hiking
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia##3
2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
3. the project-manager is in an even position##4
4. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |
