.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-12::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: rock-climbing, writing
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: martial-arts, musical
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, havana
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, skateboard
1. the person driving the skateboard is in an even position##4
2. the dunhill-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the dunhill-smoker is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Hobby         | writing   | rock-climbing |
| Movie-Genre           | martial-arts | musical    |
| Cigar   | dunhill      | havana         |
| Transport         | quad-bike   | skateboard |

