There are 2 different nationalities: mexican, american
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, tram
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the american##1
2. the mexican is on the left or right of the person eating papaya##3
3. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Food    | peach | papaya    |
| Hobby         | chess        | camping |
| Nationality         | mexican          | american     |
| Transport   | roller        | tram     |

 